OL,3,CBritish prisons crisis sees Guernsey
OL,4,Cforced to deal with more inmates
OL,6,FGuernsey's prison population has risen
OL,7,Fby 14%, with the Channel Islands
OL,8,Fblocked from transferring inmates to
OL,9,Fthe UK due to overcrowding there.
OL,11,FThe latest States of Guernsey Prison
OL,12,FService annual report for 2024 shows
OL,13,Fthe higher population was, at times,
OL,14,F"difficult to manage" with an increase
OL,15,Fin disciplinary issues.
OL,17,FLes Nicolles Prison currently has a
OL,18,Fcapacity of 134.
