OL,3,CBritish prisons crisis sees Guernsey
OL,4,Cforced to deal with more inmates
OL,6,F"The population remained complex, with
OL,7,Fan increase in sex offenders, women,
OL,8,Fand the continued accommodation of
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,F"In simple terms, there are
OL,12,Flimitations to men, women and children
OL,13,Fsharing facilities within a custodial
OL,14,Fenvironment.
OL,16,F"The staff response to these
OL,17,Fchallenges was excellent and they
OL,18,Fshould be recognised for their hard
OL,19,Fwork and dedication to continue to
OL,20,Fprovide a safe and secure prison
OL,21,Fthroughout the year."
