OL,3,CBritish prisons crisis sees Guernsey
OL,4,Cforced to deal with more inmates
OL,6,FThroughout 2024, a total of 171
OL,7,Fdiscipline offences were recorded,
OL,8,Fmore than double 2023, which saw only
OL,9,F67 issues.
OL,11,FThis led to an increase in the use of
OL,12,Fforce, with the report stating that 33
OL,13,Fincidents needed Prison Officers to
OL,14,Ftake this action, although only 11
OL,15,Fissues were categorised as 'violent'.
