OL,3,CBritish prisons crisis sees Guernsey
OL,4,Cforced to deal with more inmates
OL,6,FThe Prison Governor says some inmates
OL,7,Fwho were meant to be transferred off-
OL,8,Fisland "posed significant security
OL,9,Fissues resulting in disciplinary
OL,10,Fbreaches", but added most offences
OL,11,Fwere "relatively minor in nature".
OL,13,FHe explains: "The increase in
OL,14,Fadjudication awards from 2023 to 2024
OL,15,Fis a result of several charges being
OL,16,Flaid for single incidents involving a
OL,17,Fsmall number of prisoners.
OL,19,F"There has also been an increased
OL,20,Fnumber of charges dismissed, which has
OL,21,Finflated the total figure.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
