OL,3,CBritish prisons crisis sees Guernsey
OL,4,Cforced to deal with more inmates
OL,6,F"While most incidents are resolved
OL,7,Fwithout the need for force, there are
OL,8,Ftimes when Officers must step in as a
OL,9,Flast resort to intervene."
OL,11,FThe report did highlight some
OL,12,Fimprovements in the prison that have
OL,13,Fbeen made over the past year.
OL,15,FInjuries to both inmates and staff
OL,16,Fhave been minimal, with the prison
OL,17,Ftraining four new prison officers.
