OL,3,CBritish prisons crisis sees Guernsey
OL,4,Cforced to deal with more inmates
OL,6,FSeveral prison facility projects were
OL,7,Falso completed, including shower
OL,8,Frefurbishments and improvements to the
OL,9,Fheating supply, window replacement,
OL,10,Fand general alarm systems.
OL,12,FThe report also found that 95% of the
OL,13,Fprisoners attend work, and 75% are
OL,14,Finvolved with some type of education.
OL,16,FCollectively, inmates gained 145
OL,17,Fqualifications and awards, with five
OL,18,Fenrolled on Open University Degrees.
