OL,3,CBritish prisons crisis sees Guernsey
OL,4,Cforced to deal with more inmates
OL,6,FThe Governor concluded: "I'm pleased
OL,7,Fand satisfied with the performance of
OL,8,FGuernsey Prison throughout 2024.
OL,10,F"There have been some challenges
OL,11,Fthroughout the year; despite these
OL,12,Fobstacles, we have delivered a safe
OL,13,Fand efficient prison, which has
OL,14,Ffulfilled its role in reducing
OL,15,Freoffending and assisting in public
OL,16,Fprotection."
